    <CMUI_CheckBox name="chkColReversed" id="47214810-54da-4142-8201-0dbe88c37670">
        <alignment>1</alignment>
        <caption>Plan Reversed Within Row/Column</caption>
        <transparent/>
        <fontSize>8.25</fontSize>
        <foreColor>-2147483640</foreColor>
        <parent name="grpYard"/>
        <parentBottomOffset>7</parentBottomOffset>
        <parentRightOffset>130</parentRightOffset>
        <show3D>3</show3D>
        <tabIndex>643</tabIndex>
        <tabStop/>
        <backColor>-2147483633</backColor>
        <bubbleHelp>STRADDLE STACKS:
Containers that are in a straddle stack, have a row and a column co ordinate. 
Containers are planned from top left to bottom right through the rows and columns. 
Tick this to plan containers from top right to bottom left in the grid. i.e. reverse the columns.

FORK LIFT and RTG STACKS:
Containers that are in a FL or RTG stack, have a row and a column co ordinate. 
Containers are planned from top to bottom, left to right through the columns and rows.
Tick this to plan containers from bottom to top, left to right through the columns and rows. i.e. reverse the rows. 
</bubbleHelp>
        <enabled/>
        <height>17</height>
        <left>26</left>
        <top>226</top>
        <visible/>
        <width>234</width>
    </CMUI_CheckBox>
